channel.title: Compile Error! Please help! :( With Pictures
channel.description:
Hello! My name is Jennifer and I am very new to coding Runescape Private servers. I've been trying to fix my compile.bat button for days, but it will not work :(
I need all of your help to help me work on my server. ALL help is appreciated very much. Thanks.
I'm using Eudora World v2.0 Source (Project Insanity Base) - http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,457332.0.html
Here is my compiling error.
[IMG]http://i820.photobucket.com/albums/zz125/Coder_Kai/errorcompile.png[/img]
I'm using windows vista.
Here's the compile file as a .txt.
[IMG]http://i820.photobucket.com/albums/zz125/Coder_Kai/compilertest.png[/img]
My server will run fine, but there's no point in it if I can't customize or make any changes to it. Please help me fix this and I will gladly appreciate it.
Please help :( i'm new with this and need desperate help
